  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de DejaGnu</title>
    <para>Installez <application>DejaGnu</application> en lançant les commandes
    suivantes&nbsp;:</para>
<screen>
<userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
makeinfo --html --no-split -o doc/dejagnu.html doc/dejagnu.texi &amp;&amp;
makeinfo --plaintext       -o doc/dejagnu.txt  doc/dejagnu.texi</userinput>
</screen>
   <para>Pour tester l'installation, lancez <command>make check</command>.</para>
    <para>Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>&nbsp;:</para>
<screen role="root">
<userinput>make install &amp;&amp;
install -v -dm755   /usr/share/doc/dejagnu-&dejagnu-version; &amp;&amp;
install -v -m644    doc/dejagnu.{html,txt}                     /usr/share/doc/dejagnu-&dejagnu-version;</userinput>
</screen>
  </sect2>
